
### Quotation Management API Tests
###
### SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
### 1. Update @token with a valid JWT token
### 2. Update @companyId and @clientId with valid MongoDB ObjectIds
### 3. Run test #1 first to generate a quotation number
### 4. Run test #2 to create a quotation and copy the returned ID to @quotationId
### 5. Execute tests in sequence for best results
###
### TEST STRUCTURE:
### - Tests 1-19: Core CRUD operations
### - Tests 20-30: Enhanced features (approval, email, conversion)
### - Tests 31-45: Edge cases and complex scenarios
### - Tests V1-V10: Validation and error handling
###

