### 1. Generate Quotation Number
GET {{baseUrl}}/quotations/preview-number
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Create New Quotation (Enhanced)
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

